      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DARRA LAGO (1) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (24.46) at this track behind Strop in a Bottom Up - Restricted Win. Has the pace to be prominent. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from three starts. One of the leading chances. THOUGHT OF THAT (4) jumped from out wide and had a clear run, crossing to the lead and holding on for a placing when second (25.87) at Shepparton in a Bottom Up - Restricted Win over 450m. Expected to be in the finish again. BRONELLY TIMMY (7) was below best at his last couple, the latest finishing seventh at Ballarat, but was among the placings at Shepparton three back. Can turn it around this time. MAISEY MARY (2) is likely to have admirers.",
